rows.label: qst005601_msg001
rows.name: I guess random guessing won't work...

rows.label: qst005601_msg002
rows.name:
We might get lucky if we try enough
times, but it would take a while.

rows.label: qst005601_msg004
rows.name:
I think there must be an
ancient text that mentions
this ancient stone tablet.

rows.label: qst005601_msg005
rows.name:
You're right... It might be
faster to find some books
and look for clues again.

rows.label: qst005601_msg006
rows.name: Can I ask the mercenaries for help too?

rows.label: qst005601_msg007
rows.name:
Of course! Let's find some clues to
solve the mystery of this tablet!
